        nigel_lambert: "There could be no better way to explore into the real India, away from the tourist areas and into the heart of Indian reality, than on the world famous Royal Enfield. These bikes are just so perfectly suited to the location, and sound as cool as they look. This should be a bucket list adventure for any type of biker.",
