        peter_hofmann: "It was a very nice motorcycle tour in a fascinating country. In the middle of real life. The routes were very well chosen. The daily stages were just right, not too short or too long. The breaks during the day tours were sufficient and very original. The accommodations were very well selected. We were very well looked after by the team. We felt very safe at all times.",
