            p2: "The following day the two started their motorbikes and Pratish with his great feel for relaxed riding and knowledge of the local routes guided them across the area. Jo told Pratish about his experience of heavy hardships to get to the sweetest spots over the most beautiful routes and how much he´d love to make them accessible for likeminded travellers.",
